{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01CwckTyuJm77NsT7V7dkLLh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PErb6sj1WMv8jNoHVR2DN1","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Polenta Casserole.generated.21.txt","content":"POLENTA\nCASSEROLE\n\nServes 6 | Preparation 20 min | Cooking 45 min\n\nIngredients:\n\nFor the polenta:\n1 liter whole milk\n250 ml vegetable broth\n100 grams butter\n100 grams polenta (cornmeal)\n50 grams Parmesan cheese, grated\nSalt and white pepper\n\nFor the filling:\n300 grams mixed mushrooms, sliced\n2 medium onions, diced\n200 grams spinach, roughly chopped\n100 grams mozzarella cheese, shredded\n2 tablespoons olive oil\n3 cloves garlic, minced\nFresh thyme\nSalt and pepper\n\nInstructions:\n\n1. First, prepare the polenta. Heat milk and vegetable broth in\na large saucepan over medium heat. When it reaches a gentle simmer,\nslowly whisk in the polenta, stirring constantly to avoid lumps.\n\n2. Continue stirring for about 20-25 minutes until the polenta\nbecomes thick and creamy. Stir in the butter and Parmesan cheese.\nSeason with salt and pepper. Pour into a greased casserole dish\nand let cool slightly.\n\n3. Heat olive oil in a large skillet. Sauté the onions until\nsoftened, then add the mushrooms and garlic. Cook until mushrooms\nrelease their liquid and become golden. Add the spinach and cook\nuntil wilted. Season with salt, pepper, and thyme.\n\n4. Preheat oven to 180°C. Spread the mushroom mixture over the\npolenta base. Top with mozzarella cheese.\n\n5. Bake for 20-25 minutes until the cheese is melted and golden.\nLet rest for 5 minutes before serving.\n\nChef's Note: This dish is best served hot with a simple green salad.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":64602,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":64602},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34d40c09-863c-409f-994a-593ba34b4bf7","uuid":"fa7cfacf-1e2a-48be-a865-0091379a1951"}
